query:
SELECT 
  s.id,
  s.blingOrderId,
  s.quantity,
  s.saleDate,
  o.orderNumber,
  o.status
FROM sales s
JOIN products p ON s.productId = p.id
LEFT JOIN orders o ON s.blingOrderId = o.blingId
WHERE p.code = '36543'
  AND s.saleDate >= '2025-09-01'
  AND s.saleDate < '2025-10-01'
ORDER BY s.saleDate
LIMIT 20
